Prerequisites

bash# System requirements
- Ubuntu 22.04 LTS (recommended) or Windows 11 WSL2
- RAM: 16GB minimum (32GB recommended for full AI)
- Storage: 100GB SSD
- GPU: Optional (NVIDIA for faster local LLM)
- Internet: Optional (offline mode available)

Quick Start

bash# 1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/smartcare-hospital.git
cd smartcare-hospital

# 2. Run the installation script
chmod +x scripts/install.sh
./scripts/install.sh

# 3. Install Ollama for offline AI
curl -fsSL https://ollama.ai/install.sh | sh
ollama pull llama3
ollama pull phi3

# 4. Set up environment variables
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your configuration

# 5. Start all services
docker-compose up -d

# 6. Access the platform
# Frontend: http://localhost:3000
# API Docs: http://localhost:8000/docs
# Admin: http://localhost:3000/admin

